PREAMBLE

This software ("CaptchaIQ Platform") is an AI research platform developed
strictly for educational, academic, and authorized security research purposes.
It is designed to study CAPTCHA robustness, explore adversarial machine
learning, support accessibility research, and serve as a portfolio
demonstration of AI systems engineering.

This license grants limited, non-commercial rights to use, study, and
contribute to this software subject to the strict conditions below.

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
