SECTION 2 — PROHIBITED USES
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

You are STRICTLY PROHIBITED from:

2.1 Using this software to bypass CAPTCHA systems on any third-party service
    without the explicit written authorization of that service's owner.
2.2 Using this software for spam, phishing, credential stuffing, or any
    form of automated abuse against third-party platforms.
2.3 Using this software to assist in unauthorized mass account creation.
2.4 Deploying this software as part of any commercial anti-CAPTCHA service
    without explicit written permission from the copyright holder.
2.5 Redistributing this software for financial gain or commercial advantage.
2.6 Removing, obscuring, or altering any copyright notices, attributions,
    or license text within this software.
2.7 Claiming original authorship of this software or its architecture.
2.8 Using the project name, logo, branding, or assets without permission.
2.9 Using this software for any activity that violates applicable law.
2.10 Using this software to violate any platform's Terms of Service.
2.11 Integrating this software into production systems targeting real users
     without appropriate authorization and ethical review.
2.12 Sharing derived works publicly without retaining this license and
     original attribution.

